Booking Workflow
Should requests be auto-approved or manually approved? ADMIN WILL APPROVE
Should the requester receive email confirmation? EMAIL THAT THE BOOKING REQ WAS RECEIVED 
Should staff be able to edit, decline, or reschedule bookings? YES 
Should donations and billing be done/paid in the selected parish? UPLOAD PROOF OR PAYMENT

User Roles
Public / Parishioner:
Submit booking
Upload documents
Check availability
Parish Staff:
View all requests
Approve / decline bookings
Manage schedules 
Can set daily limits, time slots,  mass schedules, unavailable dates (blackout)
Manage documents
Access Mass Intentions PDF
View schedule summary
Diocese Admin:
Full access and user management
Parish Admin
Full access to parish related activity and parish staff management

